arStrings.szText: "How has she survived out here, all this time?"
She's infected. I don't know why, but I've heard they're not bothered by anything out here.
The swamp doesn't harm what it thinks belongs to it.
I've been here, waiting, all these years. I never thought you'd come back, but to hear your voice again... that's all I've ever wanted.
You'll hear it every day, mother. I won't leave you, not again.
Without my friend here, I don't think I would have made it. You've helped me find home again. Thank you, and farewell.
